<gpx xmlns="http://www.topografix.com/GPX/1/1" xmlns:gpxx="http://www.garmin.com/xmlschemas/GpxExtensions/v3" creator="CALTOPO" version="1.1"><metadata><name><![CDATA[Nambe Badlands]]></name></metadata><trk><name>Nambe Badlands</name><desc>Popularity: 2/5
Difficulty: 1/5
Dates: 10/1 - 5/1
Parking: Dirt lot on the west side of NM 503 with plenty of parking.

Looking for some alone time and to feel the flow on an easier run? The Nambé Badlands is a great option. This run doesn't have much elevation gain making it a great option for a higher speed or more laid back day. 

Throughout the run you have incredible sweeping views of the Sangre de Cristos and Jemez as you roll through the Rio Grande Rift. You'll find incredible geological formations while you run in the badlands. Water and wind are rapidly eroding the Tesuque Formation, exposing spires, buttes, and hoodoos, and pinnacles. Remember to pause to take in the sound of nothing more than wind and ravens.</desc><trkseg><trkpt lat="35.92497121189809" lon="-105.96282945079156"><ele>1889.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.92496" lon="-105.96285999999998"><ele>1889.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.92507" lon="-105.96832"><ele>1884.99787528191</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.92507" lon="-105.96832"><ele>1884.99787528191</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.92507" lon="-105.96832"><ele>1884.99787528191</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.925077086770266" lon="-105.96899855893946"><ele>1879.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.925077086770266" lon="-105.96899855893946"><ele>1879.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.92511" lon="-105.97215"><ele>1877.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.92511" lon="-105.97215"><ele>1877.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.92511" lon="-105.97215"><ele>1877.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.92508" lon="-105.97258999999997"><ele>1874.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.92511" lon="-105.97363999999999"><ele>1877.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.92515" lon="-105.97406999999998"><ele>1877.070103906438</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.92518" lon="-105.97411999999997"><ele>1878.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.92518" lon="-105.97411999999997"><ele>1878.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.92552" lon="-105.97483"><ele>1879.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.92552" lon="-105.97483"><ele>1879.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.92552" lon="-105.97483"><ele>1879.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.9257" lon="-105.97618"><ele>1879.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.92599" lon="-105.97679"><ele>1879.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.926" lon="-105.97707000000003"><ele>1880.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.92578" lon="-105.97753"><ele>1877.0</ele></trkpt><trkpt lat="35.92576" lon="